---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../styles/how-we-import.css';
---

<BaseLayout title="How We Import - Our Process">
  <section class="import-hero section" style="background: var(--bg-light);">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>How We Import</h1>
      <p class="lead">Transparent Process from Source to Your Door</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="process-section section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-title">
        <h2>Our Import Process</h2>
        <p>From selection to delivery, we ensure quality at every step</p>
      </div>

      <div class="process-steps">
        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-number">1</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Product Selection</h3>
            <p>We carefully research and select products based on quality, demand, and value. Our team in USA and Canada identifies the best products from trusted suppliers.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-number">2</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Purchase (USA/Canada)</h3>
            <p>Our brother in the USA and sister in Canada handle purchasing directly from suppliers. We buy in bulk to ensure competitive pricing and consistent availability.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-number">3</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Consolidation & Shipping</h3>
            <p>Products are consolidated at shipping points and sent via reliable freight forwarders experienced in shipping to Cameroon. We work with trusted logistics partners.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-number">4</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Customs & Clearance</h3>
            <p>We handle all import documentation, obtain necessary certificates (PECAE compliance), and ensure smooth customs clearance. All duties and taxes are properly calculated and paid.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-number">5</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Warehousing</h3>
            <p>Products are stored in secure facilities with proper inventory management. We track expiry dates, maintain quality standards, and organize by category for easy access.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-number">6</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Sales & Distribution</h3>
            <p>Finally, products reach you through our retail channels - online, social media, or physical locations. We ensure timely delivery and customer satisfaction.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="compliance-section section" style="background: var(--bg-light);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem;">Compliance & Quality Assurance</h2>
      <div class="compliance-grid">
        <div class="compliance-item">
          <h3>✅ Legal Compliance</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Proper business registration in Cameroon</li>
            <li>Valid import license</li>
            <li>All required certificates (PECAE)</li>
            <li>Complete customs documentation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="compliance-item">
          <h3>✅ Quality Control</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Product verification before shipping</li>
            <li>Expiry date tracking</li>
            <li>Proper storage conditions</li>
            <li>Regular quality checks</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="compliance-item">
          <h3>✅ Transparency</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Clear pricing with no hidden costs</li>
            <li>Product origin information</li>
            <li>Import date tracking</li>
            <li>Batch/shipment traceability</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="import-info section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="info-grid">
        <div class="info-card">
          <h3>Customs Duties</h3>
          <p>Duties vary by product category (0-30%) according to CEMAC Common External Tariff. We factor all costs into our transparent pricing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card"> 
          <h3>VAT</h3>
          <p>All imports are subject to 19.25% VAT as per Cameroonian regulations. This is included in our final pricing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
          <h3>Shipping Time</h3>
          <p>Typical shipping time from USA/Canada to Cameroon is 4-8 weeks depending on the shipping method and customs clearance.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section section" style="background: var(--primary-color); color: white;">
    <div class="container" style="text-align: center;">
      <h2 style="color: white;">Have Questions About Our Process?</h2>
      <p style="margin: 1rem 0 2rem; font-size: 1.1rem;">We're happy to explain our import process in detail</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn" style="background: white; color: var(--primary-color);">Contact Us</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

